{"about_the_game":"Trials of Fire is a tactical, deck-building adventure game set in a fantasy world in ruin.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/ToF_HeroLoop_v1.png?t=1729043034\" /><br><br>Savage combat and tough decisions await in the unforgiving wastelands of Ashe.<br><br>Trials of Fire combines overworld exploration, multi-character combat and loot linked deck-building to create fresh strategic options on every run. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/TrialsOfFire_SShot_SPSpkr_v3.jpg?t=1729043034\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Content added during Early Access</h2><br>9 Playable Heroes<br>4 Game Modes + 1 Seasonal Quest<br>4 Lore Quests<br>345 Skill Cards<br>220 Items<br>42 Legendary Items<br>294 Narrative Encounters<br>56 Enemy Types<br>14 Bosses<br>40 Landmarks<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/Features_ENG_v2.png?t=1729043034\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/Alchy_Header_v1.png?t=1729043034\" /><br><br>Issue combat commands to each Hero based on their cards. <br>The combination of 3 Hero decks presents new and interesting challenges in every fight.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/Sshot_CallLightning1.png?t=1729043034\" /><br><br>Movement and positional play are critical to survival in combat.<br>Use powerful card synergies to combine the unique abilities of your three heroes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/Witch_Header_v1.png?t=1729043034\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/Sshot_Inventory1.png?t=1729043034\" /><br><br>Outside of combat encounters, the party's loadout of weapons, items and gear can be swapped or upgraded.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/Sshot_LongShot_v1.png?t=1729043034\" /><br><br>New items and weapons are discovered while exploring the vast overworld of Ashe.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/Warlord_Header_v1.png?t=1729043034\" /><br><br>Traverse an immense overworld map and author a unique adventure in a dangerous hunt for resources critical to the survival of Terralin. <br><br>Every journey you take will be a Trial.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1038370/extras/TrialsOfFire_SShot_Assassin_v2.jpg?t=1729043034\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Milk Run","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1038370/cd6148bd17cd21ca76d83f13e35546f644d6a993.jpg"},{"name":"Gauntlet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1038370/5862d64381e3e9189939ec9145c420e19995ba7e.jpg"},{"name":"Trial of Fire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1038370/f52f5b0eb1d473e22b6f9270f718ff7ca44e995c.jpg"},{"name":"Scraped Through","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1038370/674836be4d15c52e5a43776969f145ea41083cd5.jpg"},{"name":"Assassin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1038370/c9fd3c36a340be57b7129777acb04e59d07f7295.jpg"},{"name":"Awoken","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1038370/8166464635f984cb338712aecb4c4f5056f4a581.jpg"},{"name":"Ascended","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1038370/6935042ac74989ab89b7dadaa6aa6858445f74f9.jp